<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MLA – Medical Life Alarm | Campaign Training</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0A1628;
    --teal: #00B5CC;
    --teal-light: #00D4F0;
    --gold: #F5A623;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --off-white: #F0F6FA;
    --muted: #8BA3B8;
    --card-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    --border: rgba(0,181,204,0.25);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
  }

  /* ── SLIDE CONTAINER ── */
  .deck {
    position: relative;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
  }

  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 60px;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transform: translateX(80px);
    transition: opacity 0.55s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1), transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  }

  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: all;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  .slide.exit {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-80px);
  }

  /* ── BACKGROUND PATTERNS ── */
  .bg-pattern {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .slide > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* ── SLIDE 1: TITLE ── */
  #slide-1 {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0A1628 0%, #0D2140 50%, #0A1628 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  #slide-1 .hero-logo {
    width: 90px; height: 90px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--teal-light));
    border-radius: 24px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0,181,204,0.4);
    animation: pulse-glow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-glow {
    0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0,181,204,0.4); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 100px rgba(0,181,204,0.7); }
  }

  #slide-1 h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 88px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -3px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--white) 40%, var(--teal-light));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  #slide-1 .subtitle {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  #slide-1 .tagline {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(0,181,204,0.15);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 10px 28px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--teal-light);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── SLIDE HEADER ── */
  .slide-header {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .slide-num {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .slide-num::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    max-width: 60px;
  }

  .slide-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 44px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .slide-title span {
    color: var(--teal-light);
  }

  /* ── CONTENT WRAPPER ── */
  .content-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
  }

  /* ── BULLET CARDS ── */
  .bullet-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .bullet-grid.cols-2 {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }

  .bullet-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }

  .bullet-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0,181,204,0.1);
  }

  .bullet-icon {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    min-width: 38px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,181,204,0.2), rgba(0,212,240,0.1));
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }

  .bullet-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #C8DDE8;
  }

  .bullet-card strong {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* ── FEATURE ICONS ── */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .feat-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  }

  .feat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: rgba(0,181,204,0.12);
  }

  .feat-icon {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--teal-light));
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }

  .feat-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .feat-card p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── PRODUCT CARDS ── */
  .product-cols {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .product-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 36px 32px;
  }

  .product-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--teal);
    background: rgba(0,181,204,0.08);
  }

  .price-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .price-main {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--teal-light);
  }

  .price-cross {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .product-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .product-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* ── FAQ STYLE ── */
  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-q {
    padding: 18px 24px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--teal-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .faq-a {
    padding: 0 24px 18px 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #C8DDE8;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 16px;
  }

  /* ── STAT CALLOUT ── */
  .stat-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .stat-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,181,204,0.15), rgba(0,181,204,0.05));
    border: 1px solid var(--teal);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 32px;
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--teal-light);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── NAVIGATION ── */
  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 40px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,22,40,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
  }

  .nav-btn {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-btn:hover {
    background: var(--teal);
    border-color: var(--teal);
  }

  .nav-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .nav-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-dot.active {
    background: var(--teal-light);
    width: 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .nav-counter {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    min-width: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── SLIDE-SPECIFIC BACKGROUNDS ── */
  #slide-2, #slide-3 { background: #0A1628; }
  #slide-4 { background: linear-gradient(150deg, #0A1628, #0D1E35); }
  #slide-5, #slide-6 { background: #0A1628; }
  #slide-7, #slide-8 { background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0A1628, #071220); }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    width: 60px; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), transparent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ── SLIDE 8 END ── */
  #slide-8 { text-align: center; }
  #slide-8 .end-icon {
    width: 100px; height: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--teal-light));
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(0,181,204,0.5);
  }

  #slide-8 h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--white) 30%, var(--teal-light));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  #slide-8 p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── DECORATIVE ORBIT CIRCLES ── */
  .orbit {
    position: fixed;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,181,204,0.08);
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: spin linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    from { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(360deg); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Decorative circles -->
<div class="orbit" style="width:700px;height:700px;top:50%;left:50%;animation-duration:40s;"></div>
<div class="orbit" style="width:1000px;height:1000px;top:50%;left:50%;animation-duration:60s;animation-direction:reverse;"></div>

<div class="deck" id="deck">

  <!-- SLIDE 1: TITLE -->
  <div class="slide active" id="slide-1">
    <div class="hero-logo">
      <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none">
        <path d="M22 6C14 6 8 12 8 20C8 28 22 40 22 40C22 40 36 28 36 20C36 12 30 6 22 6Z" fill="white" opacity="0.9"/>
        <path d="M17 20H27M22 15V25" stroke="#00B5CC" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>MLA</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Medical Life Alarm</div>
    <div class="tagline">Campaign Training</div>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 2: INTRODUCTION -->
  <div class="slide" id="slide-2">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <div class="slide-num">02 — Introduction</div>
      <h2 class="slide-title">What Are <span>Medical Alert</span> Devices?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content-wrap">
      <div class="bullet-grid cols-2">
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>What they are:</strong> Wearable devices that connect users to emergency help at the push of a button — 24/7.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M20 21a8 8 0 10-16 0"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>2 shapes:</strong> A <strong>necklace</strong> worn around the neck, or a <strong>smartwatch</strong> worn around the wrist.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>Target users:</strong> Seniors, people with chronic illnesses, post-surgery patients, and individuals living alone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>Key benefit:</strong> Peace of mind for users <em>and</em> their families — independence with a safety net.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 3: WHY IMPORTANT -->
  <div class="slide" id="slide-3">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <div class="slide-num">03 — The Problem</div>
      <h2 class="slide-title">Why Are They <span>Important?</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content-wrap">
      <div class="stat-row">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">1 in 4</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Seniors over 65 fall each year — falls are the #1 cause of injury</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">24/7</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Emergency help available with just one button press</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bullet-grid cols-2">
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>Immediate response</strong> reduces complications and saves lives in critical moments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>Live at home longer</strong> — provides confidence to stay independent without constant supervision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>Reduces stress and guilt</strong> — families know their loved ones are protected at all times.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bullet-card">
          <div class="bullet-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4F0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 9h6M9 12h6M9 15h4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><strong>Prevents nursing home placements</strong> by providing reliable, 24/7 safety at home.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 4: FEATURES -->
  <div class="slide" id="slide-4">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <div class="slide-num">04 — Device Capabilities</div>
      <h2 class="slide-title">Features of <span>the Device</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content-wrap">
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>24/7 Emergency Monitoring</h4>
          <p>Live operators available around the clock, every day of the year.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Auto Fall Detection</h4>
          <p>Automatically alerts operators if a fall is detected — even if the button isn't pressed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v3M12 19v3M4.22 4.22l2.12 2.12M17.66 17.66l2.12 2.12M2 12h3M19 12h3M4.22 19.78l2.12-2.12M17.66 6.34l2.12-2.12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>GPS Tracking</h4>
          <p>Works everywhere across the US — outdoor safety with precise location reporting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Two-Way Communication</h4>
          <p>Speak directly to a live operator through the pendant or watch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M12 2a7 7 0 017 7c0 5-7 13-7 13S5 14 5 9a7 7 0 017-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Water-Resistant</h4>
          <p>Wearable as pendant or wristband — safe in the shower and daily use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Long Battery Life</h4>
          <p>Easy charging with extended battery life — always ready when you need it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Vitals Monitoring</h4>
          <p>Smartwatch tracks blood pressure, heart rate, and oxygen saturation in real time.</p>
        </div>
